    <abstract>
      <t>This document presents a number of considerations regarding evaluating Information-Centric Networking (ICN) and sheds some light on the impact of ICN on network security.  It also surveys the evaluation tools currently available to researchers in the ICN area and provides suggestions regarding methodology and metrics.
